    "description": "在不远的未来，人类终于征服了其他星系。现在，他们正致力于寻找新的土地来建设高效水培农场并在那里种植农作物。<br>与您的机器人团队哔啵 179 一起踏上新的旅程。建造和管理新的工厂，培植各种美味的植物，并克服外星球的种种神秘挑战，努力生存下来。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 🚀  建造您的太空基地  🪐</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/743ce07ee6fce055355200ce12d853f0.poster.avif?t=1706878525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/743ce07ee6fce055355200ce12d853f0.webm?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/743ce07ee6fce055355200ce12d853f0.mp4?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你已经登陆了一个新的星球，现在是时候逐步建造您的工厂了。设置房间和走廊，并添加水培机、实验室设备和装饰品，为您的定居点增添活力并开始发展您的业务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌱 种植植物 🍓</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/5a9a45642ec76872dfd94a0a543d8830.poster.avif?t=1706878525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/5a9a45642ec76872dfd94a0a543d8830.webm?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/5a9a45642ec76872dfd94a0a543d8830.mp4?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从新鲜的绿色生菜到香甜可口的蓝香瓜：您可以选择来自地球的原生植物，或是培植外星球的替代品。但是要注意，您必须为它们的成长创造适宜的条件。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚙️ 照管好您的工厂和机器人 🤖</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/a074c8bc2a739ebad5713a620d529d2e.poster.avif?t=1706878525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/a074c8bc2a739ebad5713a620d529d2e.webm?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/a074c8bc2a739ebad5713a620d529d2e.mp4?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果您想扩大自己的商业版图，就需要仔细规划每一步行动。了解水培机的工作原理、如何销售产品以获得利润以及如何提高产量。最后，还有注意机器人们的福祉：为他们创造一个元气满满的空间，以供其休息、交际和充电。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/c89bad5100ae1e11494d8a1bd0e01d25.poster.avif?t=1706878525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/c89bad5100ae1e11494d8a1bd0e01d25.webm?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1613470/extras/c89bad5100ae1e11494d8a1bd0e01d25.mp4?t=1706878525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>那么，听好了。是否已准备好在外太空开启新的冒险？",
